config DVB_AMLOGIC
	tristate "Amlogic DVB/TS Demultiplexer"
	depends on DVB_CORE && OF && HAS_DMA
	select REGMAP_MMIO
        help
          Amlogic DVB/TS hardware demultiplexer driver for 'Meson' SoC
          family devices, e.g. GXBB/GXL/GXM/G12A/G12B/SM1. Supports
	  hardware PID filtering, section DMA, and DVR recording.

          To compile as a module, say M.
